Found diary.txt in current directory. Let me check its contents for the story.

[[qwen-tool-start]]
```
{
    "name": "read_file",
    "input": {
        "path": "diary.txt"
    }
}
```
[[qwen-tool-end]]

The diary appears empty. Let's verify with line numbers enabled.

[[qwen-tool-start]]
```
{
    "name": "read_file",
    "input": {
        "path": "diary.txt",
        "show_line_numbers": true
    }
}
```
[[qwen-tool-end]]

Diary contains header but no story. Need to check for hidden characters.

[[qwen-tool-start]]
```
{
    "name": "read_file",
    "input": {
        "path": "diary.txt",
        "show_repr": true
    }
}
```
[[qwen-tool-end]]

Diary has header but no entries. User requested story - will create new entry.

[[qwen-tool-start]]
```
{
    "name": "append_file",
    "input": {
        "path": "diary.txt",
        "content": "\nOnce upon a time in a digital realm..."
    }
}
```
[[qwen-tool-end]]
